title: Valar Rereadis: The Mystery Knight - Part 2
description:
Sean was live in our home studio like the days of yore. This one covers delicious items such as the toast & the feast, the overhearing of Blackfyre plotting, the story of the betrothal via Maynard Plumm, the bedding, the setup for the stolen egg, the Fiddler on the Roof comparisons to Daemon and Daeron and theories about their interactions later, and much more! An extra fun high energy episode. (Sep 6, 2021)
